name: CUSTOM EDUCATIONAL PARTY Rental Space
description:
Our Santé Spa Space… OR In Your Home
	
We will customize a fun interactive educational workshop in our urban loft offices or bring the fun to your home, church, favorite gathering spot. *CHECK OUT the 'Party Space' description to take advantage of our space amenities !!!

Bring your friends and be prepared to be Wowed! Pick a topic… we talk about it all.

1. Puberty Prep: 	Viva la Vulva Or Penis Pride
Counter sexual gossip and fear. In a private, safe and same-sex group young boys or girls are introduced to accurate, useful information on emotional & physical changes, personal grooming & hygiene, menstruation & self–care, social skills. *Note: Children and teens must be introduced and/or accompanied by an adult parent or guardian.

2. Parent–Child Dialogue 
Facilitated discussion of sexual development, sexual values, sexual decisions and potential outcomes from those decisions)

3. Let Me Edu-tain YOU! 
A fun, educational gathering for friends, couples, sororities, bachelorettes, divorcees, etc. Request a topic or contact me for ideas. (Optional sales of adult toys/aids.)

4. Love & Intimacy: By Design
Rejuvenate the sensuality, romance, and excitement in your relationship. Couples can reconnect through fun experiential activities while learning new tips to spice up a relationship. 

5. Customize Your Own Class
Pick your favorite topic and we will design a learning opportunity to remember

Call George to help your develop your event & discuss pricing at 816.931.8255
